  "description": "CarbonFLTR is a client side item filter mod who prevents you taking dropped item you don't want to pickup.",
  "body": "# **Argon**\n\n### __**What is this ?**__\n\nCarbonFLTR is a client side item filter mod who prevents you taking dropped item you don't want to pickup.\n\nIs a client side mod who didn't work on server cuz is everytime the server who manage when you pickup an item.\n\n### __**How it work ?**__\n\nYou can use the command below to add item to the filter.\n\n**```/carbonfilter add minecraft:netherrack```**\n\n\nAnd you can use the command below to remove item from the filter.\n\n**```/carbonfilter remove minecraft:netherrack```**\n\n## Download\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/carbonfltr\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/v3/assets/cozy/available/modrinth_64h.png\" alt=\"Modrinth Badge\" title=\"Modrinth Badge\" width=\"190\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://fabricmc.net/\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/v3/assets/cozy/supported/fabric_64h.png\" alt=\"Fabric Badge\" title=\"Fabric Badge\" width=\"190\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://minecraftforge.net/\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/v3/assets/cozy/unsupported/forge_64h.png\" alt=\"Fabric Badge\" title=\"Fabric Badge\" width=\"190\" /></a>\n\n<a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/v3/assets/cozy/requires/cloth-config-api_64h.png\" alt=\"Cloth Config API Badge\" title=\"Cloth Config API Badge\" width=\"190\" /></a>\n\n## Other\n\n<a href=\"https://discord.gg/NvP7acJXSR\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/v3/assets/cozy/social/discord-singular_64h.png\" alt=\"Fabric Badge\" title=\"Fabric Badge\" width=\"190\" /></a>\n<a href=\"https://www.paypal.me/monspropre\"><img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/intergrav/devins-badges/v3/assets/cozy/donate/paypal-singular_64h.png\" alt=\"Fabric Badge\" title=\"Fabric Badge\" width=\"190\" /></a>",
